a%3E%20Israeli%20troops%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20opened%20fire%20and%20that%20they%20deliberately%20targeted%20the%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20also%20emerged%20on%20Thursday%2C%20however%2C%20was%20a%20possibility%20that%20some%20could%20not%20process%3A%20One%2C%20that%20the%20IDF%20was%20telling%20the%20truth%2C%20this%20time%2C%20when%20it%20blamed%20the%20explosion%20near%20the%20Ahli%20Arab%20Hospital%20on%20a%20misfired%20rocket%20from%20Islamic%20Jihad%3B%20and%20two%2C%20that%20the%20international%20media%20had%20actually%20challenged%20the%20assertions%20of%20Israel%2C%20a%20Western%20ally%2C%20and%20in%20this%20case%20deferred%20to%20the%20claims%20of%20Hamas%20authorities%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20imagine%20the%20headlines%20if%20Putin%20had%20bombed%20a%20hospital%20in%20Kharkiv%2C%20killing%20500%20people%2C%20many%20of%20them%20kids%2C%20and%20then%20blamed%20it%20on%20the%20Ukrainians%2C%26quot%3B%20Yanis%20Vaourfakis%2C%20a%20leftist%20economist%20and%20Greek%20politician%2C%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20makes%20Vlad%20happier%20than%20watching%20the%20West's%20touching%20attempts%20to%20overtake%20his%20callous%20cynicism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20bombed%20hospitals%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Syria%2C%20and%20its%20denials%20have%20been%20viewed%20as%20dubious%20for%20a%20simple%20reason%3A%20If%20something%20falls%20from%20the%20sky%20and%20explodes%2C%20it%20is%20generally%20right%20to%20suspect%20the%20party%20with%20air%20supremacy.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20happened%20Tuesday%2C%20Israeli%20claims%20treated%20with%20a%20similar%2C%20earned%20skepticism%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0even%20before%20the%20bombing%20of%20a%20hospital%20was%20an%20established%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20knee-jerk%20response%20also%20went%20the%20other%20way.%20Before%20the%20IDF%20issued%20a%20denial%2C%20Hananya%20Naftali%2C%20a%20right-wing%20Israeli%20influencer%2C%20assumed%20Israel%20was%20responsible%20%E2%80%94%20and%20immediately%20attempted%20to%20justify%20it%3A%20A%20%26quot%3BHamas%20terrorist%20based%20inside%20a%20hospital%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20attacked%2C%20he%20posted%20on%20social%20media%2C%20killing%20a%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20of%20terrorists.%26quot%3B%20In%20this%2C%20he%20was%20indeed%20no%20different%20than%20commentators%20who%20have%20excused%20Russia's%20atrocities%3A%20projecting%20absolute%20certainty%20that%20whatever%20happened%2C%20despite%20the%20little%20we%20know%2C%20was%20for%20a%20damn%20good%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%2C%20then%2C%20were%20embarrassed%20by%20what%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eobjectively%20good%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealbeit%20startling%20news%3A%20that%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20reported%20as%20leveled%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20still%20standing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20bombed%20by%20the%20IDF%20at%20all.%20That's%20a%20conclusion%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebacked%20by%20US%20intelligence%20and%20supported%20by%20independent%20analysts%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaza-hospital-explosion-inconsistent-with-israeli-strikes-former-un-investigator-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eformer%20UN%20war%20crimes%20investigator%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bellingcat.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F18%2Fidentifying-possible-crater-from-gaza-hospital-blast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eresearchers%20at%20Bellingcat%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20the%20damage%20seen%20in%20photographs%20shared%20the%20next%20morning%C2%A0was%20not%20consistent%20with%20the%20area%20being%20struck%20in%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20French%20intelligence%20assessment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Fnews%2Ffrench-military-intel-says-no-indication-gaza-hospital-blast-was-israeli-strike-946e673e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20public%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20rejected%20claims%20of%20%26quot%3Ban%20Israeli%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20to%20indicate%26quot%3B%20the%20hospital%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20IDF%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20probable%20hypothesis%20is%20that%20a%20Palestinian%20rocket%20exploded%20with%20a%20charge%20of%20about%20five%20kilos%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%2C%20too%2C%20concluded%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0after%20an%20analysis%20of%20video%20and%20input%20from%20%26quot%3Bexperts%20with%20specialties%20in%20open-source%20intelligence%2C%20geolocation%20and%20rocketry%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20most%20likely%20cause%20of%20the%20blast%20near%20the%20hospital%20was%20a%20misfired%20rocket%2C%20not%20an%20Israeli%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20media%20(and%20others)%20have%20lessons%20to%20learn%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20fog%20of%20war%2C%20paired%20with%20social%20media%2C%20is%20a%20recipe%20for%20inaccuracy.%20We%20should%20all%20slow%20down%20and%20be%20more%20inclined%20to%20let%20the%20fog%20lift%20before%20broadcasting%20an%20unverified%20claim.%20While%20some%20may%20see%20this%20week's%20reporting%20as%20the%20product%20of%20an%20anti-Israel%20bias%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20likely%20more%20mundane%3A%20No%20news%20outlet%20wants%20to%20be%20the%20last%20one%20to%20cover%20the%20most%20important%20story%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20while%20the%20IDF's%20statements%20should%20continue%20to%20be%20viewed%20with%20healthy%20skepticism%2C%20the%20official%20sources%20in%20Gaza%20clearly%20warrant%20at%20least%20as%20much%20scrutiny%2C%20controlled%20as%20they%20are%20by%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20organization.%20Hamas%20has%20an%20incentive%20to%20blame%20anything%20bad%20that%20happens%20in%20Gaza%20on%20the%20Israeli%20state%20and%20has%20shown%20itself%20willing%20to%20fabricate%20a%20war%20crime%20%E2%80%94%20claiming%20a%20hospital%20found%20standing%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20destroyed%20the%20night%20before.%20If%20it%20wasn't%20absolutely%20clear%20before%2C%20it%20is%20today%3A%20The%20local%20health%20ministry%2C%20which%20rushed%20out%20a%20now%20seemingly%20implausible%20body%20count%2C%20answers%20to%20this%20extremist%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20this%20is%20not%20to%20deny%20that%20Palestinians%20are%20suffering%20under%20Israeli%20bombardment.%20People%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20with%20no%20connection%20to%20Hamas%2C%20can%20attest%20to%20this%2C%20and%20the%20IDF%20would%20only%20dispute%20who%20is%20ultimately%20to%20blame.%20That%20points%20to%20the%20last%20lesson%20from%20all%20this%20for%20partisans%20of%20either%20side%20and%20other%20news%20consumers%3A%20What%20happens%20in%20war%20will%20not%20always%20reaffirm%20our%20prior%20convictions.%20Assumptions%20should%20always%20be%20questioned%2C%20and%20truths%20acknowledged%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0convenient%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaza-hamas-israel-lessons-learned-hospital-bombing-media-propaganda-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697973541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652fb10b96f7540cd05f1c7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaza-hamas-israel-lessons-learned-hospital-bombing-media-propaganda-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reporters%20and%20others%20were%20quick%20to%20spread%20an%20unverified%20claim%20of%20a%20hospital%20being%20bombed%20in%20Gaza.%20We%20all%20need%20to%20be%20more%20skeptical.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cdavis%40insider.com%20(Charles%20R.%20Davis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaza-hamas-israel-lessons-learned-hospital-bombing-media-propaganda-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2