%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ukraine%20bakhmut%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6534f16896908fd7cdb4bd03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%2010th%20Mountain%20Assault%20Brigade%20of%20Ukraine%20fire%20in%20the%20Bakhmut%20District%2C%20Donetsk%20Region%20on%20September%2016%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ELibkos%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ERussia%20has%20been%20adapting%20its%20fighting%20tactics%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20retake%20a%20key%20village%2C%20Ukraine%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20spokesperson%20said%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20witnessed%20Russia%20digging%20tunnels%20for%20%26quot%3Bcamouflage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ERussia%20is%20also%20using%20remote-controlled%20vehicles%20to%20resupply%20its%20forces%20with%20ammunition%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%5D%5C%22%3ERussian%20soldiers%20are%20digging%20tunnels%20to%20sneak%20up%20Ukrainian%20positions%20without%20being%20seen%20by%20their%20lethal%20drones%2C%20a%20military%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20retake%20the%20eastern%20town%20of%20Andriivka%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20Oblast%2C%20Russian%20troops%20are%20turning%20to%20new%20tactics%2C%20Anton%20Kotsukon%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20a%20Ukrainian%20brigade%20fighting%20in%20the%20area%2C%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Avdiivka%20direction%2C%20the%20Russians%20began%20to%20use%20new%20tactics.%20They%20are%20digging%20tunnels%20closer%20to%20our%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20Kotsukon%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20translation%20by%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuromaidanpress.com%2F2023%2F09%2F10%2Frussian-military-reveals-firing-positions-while-shooting-at-ukrainian-flag-attached-to-balloons%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20the%20Ukrainian%20nongovernmental%20organization%20Euromaidan%20Press.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKotsukon%20is%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20110th%20Separate%20Mechanized%20Brigade.%20The%20brigade%20was%20crucial%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-is-sending-small-assault-units-to-attack-russia-report-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erecapturing%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3EAndriivka%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-is-sending-small-assault-units-to-attack-russia-report-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESeptember%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20tunnels%20are%20there%20for%20%26quot%3Bcamouflage%26quot%3B%20from%20Ukraine's%20surveillance%20drones%20and%20so%20that%20the%20Russians%20can%20%26quot%3Bsuddenly%20emerge%20closer%20to%20our%20positions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETunnel%20warfare%20has%20been%20practiced%20since%20Roman%20times.%20Viet%20Cong%20guerillas%20used%20a%20sophisticated%20network%20of%20tunnels%20to%20attack%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcu-chi-tunnels-unforgettable-reminder-vietnam-war-viet-cong-2023-6%5C%22%3EUS%20soldiers%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20repeatedly%20attempted%20to%20recapture%20the%20town%20in%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20offensive%20efforts%20in%20months.%20Putin's%20forces%20have%20repeatedly%20attempted%20to%20recapture%20the%20town%20in%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20offensive%20efforts%20in%20months.%20Its%20soldiers%20are%20attempting%20to%20flank%20Andriivka%20but%20are%20suffering%20serious%20losses%20due%20to%20Ukrainian%20artillery%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20drones%20have%20been%20particularly%20effective.%20A%20video%20shared%20by%20Ukraine's%20military%20last%20week%20appeared%20to%20show%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-combat-video-destruction-russian-armor-tanks-new-assault-2023-10%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERussian%20tanks%20and%20armor%20being%20destroyed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20headed%20toward%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20said%20it%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20first-person%20view%20(FPV)%20drones%2C%20US-provided%20Javelin%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles%2C%20and%20mortars%20for%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20General%20Staff%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGeneralStaff.ua%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02cqQ4a7XxvNvZHZoUa7tt9MttmDCceWGfRRRWuuf5NCsPLAz7n2HdVms9yJWh9mPFl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Friday%20that%20in%20one%20day%20of%20fighting%20in%20the%20area%2C%20nearly%20900%20Russians%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20100%20units%20of%20their%20armored%20equipment%20were%20also%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20its%20heavy%20losses%2C%20Russia%20is%20attempting%20to%20resupply%20its%20troops%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Kotsukon%20said%20that%20Russia%20is%20now%20using%20remote-controlled%20vehicles%20the%20size%20of%20cars%20to%20send%20ammunition%20to%20the%20frontlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20enough%20resources%2C%20very%20fierce%20battles%20continue%20every%20day%2C%20every%20day%20they%20throw%20new%20and%20new%20forces%20into%20the%20assaults%20%E2%80%94%20both%20personnel%20and%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20aviation%2C%20artillery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkyivindependent.com%2Fmilitary-russian-forces-use-new-tactics-remote-controlled-vehicles-in-avdiivka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20translation%20by%20the%20Kyiv%20Independent.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever