BI%20try%20not%20to%20work%20from%20there.%20I%20really%20want%20to%20create%20that%20separation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20also%20should%20still%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20get%20ready%20for%20the%20day%20even%20if%20they%20are%20working%20from%20home%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20talk%20about%20romanticizing%20their%20life%20and%20the%20little%20moments%2C%26quot%3B%20Couse%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20get%20dressed%20up%2C%20I%20pack%20my%20bag%2C%20so%20my%20laptop%20goes%20in%20my%20laptop%20cover%2C%20which%20goes%20in%20my%20bag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECouse%20also%20does%20her%20hair%20before%20logging%20on%20to%20work%20and%20also%20said%20she%20would%20sometimes%20put%20on%20shoes.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20said%20she%20doesn't%20always%20use%20the%20same%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20leave%20my%20bag%20in%20the%20kitchen%20area%20after%20work%20so%20I%20can%20grab%20it%20off%20the%20kitchen%20table%20when%20I'm%20ready%20to%20go%20into%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Couse%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWorkers%20should%20time%20block%20their%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarpineto%20said%20that%20especially%20for%20parents%2C%20having%20work%20and%20home%20balance%20is%20hard%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20balance%20is%20%26quot%3Beven%20rougher%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20delineated%20lines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20in%20eliminating%20work%20from%20home%20burnout%20is%20really%20about%20time%20blocking%2C%26quot%3B%20Carpineto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20different%20types%20of%20time%20blocking%20and%20it's%20defined%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20scheduling%20format%20that%20helps%20boost%20productivity%20by%20dividing%20your%20day%20into%20specific%20blocks%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20project-management%20software%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%2Fblog%2Fproductivity%2Fincrease-your-productivity-with-time-blocking-a-step-by-step-guide%2F%5C%22%3Emonday.co