%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6528461468f1d46f52b06af3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Shapiro%20of%20Jasper.ai%2C%20Chris%20Foltz%20of%20IBM%2C%20Lindsey%20Duran%20of%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Flavien%20Coronini%20of%20Hugging%20Face.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jasper.ai%2C%20IBM%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Hugging%20Face%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApplicants%20are%20using%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20to%20seek%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20getting%20hired.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERecruiters%20told%20Insider%20they%20caught%20candidates%20using%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20to%20write%20cover%20letters%20and%20answer%20questions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20agree%20ChatGPT%20can%20be%20useful%20in%20refining%20your%20application%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20has%20a%20human%20touch.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-roles-companies-want-ai-chatgpt-experience-salary-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKnowing%20how%20to%20use%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20could%20potentially%20help%20you%20land%20your%20next%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20you%20trust%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20to%20apply%20for%20roles%20for%20you%2C%20recruiters%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20ChatGPT%20came%20out%20almost%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-ai-job-career-ibm-nvidia-recruiters-advice-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecruitment%20leaders%20at%20Nvidia%2C%20Jasper%2C%20and%20Hugging%20Face%20seeking%20to%20fill%20their%20AI-related%20roles%20%3C%2Fa%3Esay%20they've%20noticed%20an%20uptick%20in%20job%20applicants%20using%20the%20chatbot%20to%20help%20them%20move%20through%20the%20application%20process.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%20survey%20of%20nearly%20500%2C000%20job%20seekers%20in%202021%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-ai-write-resume-chatgpt-job-search-cover-letter-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticipants%20who%20received%20%26quot%3Balgorithmic%20writing%20assistance%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20tweak%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20were%208%25%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20hired%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20those%20who%20didn't%20use%20the%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20recruiters%20say%20they%20see%20the%20value%20in%20candidates%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20strengthen%20their%20job%20applications%2C%20others%20believe%20that%20taking%20a%20chatbot's%20suggestions%20at%20face%20value%20can%20actually%20hurt%20one's%20chances%20of%20getting%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Shapiro%2C%20the%20chief%20people%20officer%20at%20Jasper%2C%20an%20AI%20marketing%20and%20writing%20software%20firm%2C%20said%20she's%20noticed%20an%20increase%20in%20job%20seekers%20using%20generative%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20generate%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20cover%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20admits%20that%20using%20ChatGPT%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bgreat'%20in%20helping%20applicants%20%26quot%3Bbrainstorm%20verbs%26quot%3B%20and%20reframe%20language%20that%20can%20%26quot%3Bbring%20a%20level%20of%20polish%20to%20their%20applications.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20notes%20that%20submitting%20AI-generated%20materials%20along%20with%20job%20applications%20can%20actually%20backfire%20if%20applicants%20don't%20review%20them%20for%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20said%20Jasper%20recruiters%20have%20interviewed%20candidates%20and%20discovered%20skills%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20that%20applicants%20said%20shouldn't%20be%20there%2C%20or%20characterizations%20they%20weren't%20familiar%20with.%20Checking%20the%20AI-generated%20materials%20to%20ensure%20they%20accurately%20reflect%20an%20applicant's%20capabilities%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20critical%20if%20ChatGPT%20is%20being%20used%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20the%20applicant%20gets%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20took%20yourself%20out%20of%20that%20process%20and%20just%20submitted%20it%2C%20that%20will%20be%20a%20problem%20down%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20%26quot%3Breally%20bad%20practice%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20used%20improperly%2C%20ChatGPT%20can%20actually%20stop%20a%20job%20applicant%20from%20moving%20forward%20in%20the%20hiring%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlavien%20Coronini%2C%20the%20talent%20acquisition%20lead%20at%20Hugging%20Face%2C%20an%20AI%20company%20behind%20tools%20like%20text-to-image%20generator%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhuggingface.co%2Fspaces%2Fgoogle%2Fsdxl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EStable%20Diffusion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20he's%20seen%20cover%20letters%20that%20were%20obviously%20generated%20by%20AI%20with%20no%20human%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20one%20cover%20letter%20that%20included%20the%20prompt%20%26quot%3BInsert%20a%20cover%20letter%20in%20order%20to%20explain%20why%20my%20background%20is%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20this%20role%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20bad%20practice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20this%20is%20a%20showstopper%2C%20because%20it%20doesn't%20really%20show%20your%20motivation%20to%20join%2C%26quot%3B%20Coronini%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20applicants%2C%20even%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20company%20disqualifying%20a%20job%20candidate%20from%20consideration%20may%20still%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20relying%20on%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20Duran%2C%20vice-president%20of%20global%20recruiting%20at%20Nvidia%2C%20said%20recruiters%20at%20the%20chip%20giant%20have%20caught%20candidates%20using%20ChatGPT%20during%20interviews%20to%20answer%20questions%20even%20though%20they%20were%20explicitly%20told%20prior%20that%20using%20AI%20for%20that%20purpose%20was%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChatGPT%20skills%20can%20boost%20your%20chances%20of%20getting%20hired%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20can%20prove%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20all%20the%20recruiters%20who%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20agreed%20that%20emphasizing%20AI%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20ChatGPT%20expertise%20%E2%80%94%20during%20the%20hiring%20process%20can%20help%20job%20seekers%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20applicant%20pool.%20But%20they%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20prove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Foltz%2C%20the%20chief%20talent%20officer%20at%20IBM%2C%20said%20applicants%20can%20increase%20their%20chances%20of%20getting%20an%20AI%20job%20by%20demonstrating%20their%20knowledge%20and%20passion%20for%20the%20subject%20during%20an%20interview.%20That%20could%20mean%20explaining%20how%20to%20apply%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20to%20workflows%2C%20taking%20%26quot%3Bindustry-recognized%26quot%3B%20online%20courses%20in%20AI%2C%20or%20staying%20up-to-date%20with%20the%20latest%20developments%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20and%20Duran%20echoed%20Foltz's%20sentiment.%20When%20interviewing%20for%20technical%20and%20non-technical%20roles%20alike%2C%20the%20Jasper%20recruiter%20expects%20candidates%20to%20be%20able%20to%20articulate%20how%20they've%20been%20experimenting%20with%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20as%20that%20shows%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20or%20not%20people%20have%20dived%20into%20this%20industry.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20Duran%20said%20she%20considers%20ChatGPT%20a%20%26quot%3Brelatively%20newer%20skill%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20company%20takes%20into%20consideration%20for%20select%20roles%2C%20though%20she%20said%20the%20strongest%20applicants%20have%20%26quot%3Bcore%20foundational%20skills%26quot%3B%20around%20programming%20and%20algorithms.%20Coronini%20suggests%20applicants%20add%20GitHub%20links%20to%20past%20AI%20projects%20in%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20a%20human%20touch%20to%20AI-generated%20job%20apps%E2%80%94%20or%20risk%20getting%20replaced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20ways%20job%20seekers%20can%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20elevate%20their%20applications%20without%20them%20feeling%20like%20they're%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshley%20Couto%2C%20a%20self-proclaimed%20AI%20consultant%2C%20previously%20wrote%20for%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-cover-letter-chatgpt-template-prompts-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20applicants%20can%20most%20effectively%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20write%20a%20cover%20letter%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20specifying%20what%20it%20needs%20to%20contain%20and%20instructing%20the%20chatbot%20to%20revise%20certain%20sentences%20or%20paragraphs%20repeatedly%20until%20they%20reflect%20the%20applicant's%20unique%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20touch%20may%20be%20what%20stops%20job%20candidates%20from%20getting%20replaced%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20grappling%20with%20the%20content%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20feel%20like%20you%20could%20represent%20it%20yourself%2C%20you%20can't%20break%20down%20the%20logic%20behind%20it%2C%20I%20think%20we%20should%20probably%20just%20hire%20the%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-recruitment-jobs-candidates-applications-employment-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697969075000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653289eebe9edfa8eda5d151%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-recruitment-jobs-candidates-applications-employment-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recruiters%20say%20more%20candidates%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs%20and%20even%20answer%20questions%20during%20interviews.%20Here's%20why%