%20into%20unwelcome%20refugees.%20One%20large%20family%20lived%20in%20a%20huge%20%3Cem%3Ekothi%3C%2Fem%3E%20next%20to%20ours.%20They%20were%20luckier%20than%20many%2C%20and%20had%20done%20very%20well%20with%20the%20land%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20government%20had%20granted%20them%20in%20the%20terai%20region%20as%20compensation.%20However%2C%20memories%20of%20the%20Partition%20and%20a%20sudden%20loss%20of%20centuries%20old%20roots%20had%20driven%20several%20members%20in%20the%20family%20to%20lose%20their%20sanity.%20Even%20though%20they%20now%20had%20several%20kothis%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CFaaram%20Haus%E2%80%9D%2C%20faces%20of%20their%20women%20remained%20perennially%20sad%20with%20vacant%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20279px)%2085vw%2C%20279px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22279%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWar%2C%20we%20were%20learning%20slowly%2C%20is%20a%20terrible%20thing%20that%20turns%20men%20into%20beasts%2C%20women%20into%20zombies%20and%20children%20into%20scarred%20and%20introverted%20human%20beings%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20lives.%20Most%20of%20our%20classmates%20in%20a%20sparsely%20furnished%20missionary%20school%20came%20from%20small%20towns%20or%20rural%20areas%2C%20and%20admissions%20were%20granted%20to%20all%20who%20had%20certifiably%20cleared%20the%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20school%20benches%20in%20Shahjahanpur%20were%20long%20and%20hard%20and%20Mohan%2C%20a%20poor%20boy%20from%20a%20refugee%20family%2C%20sat%20to%20my%20left%20on%20one%20of%20those.%20He%20had%20a%20thin%20pockmarked%20face%20and%20had%20lost%20an%20eye%20when%20a%20pellet%20gun%20was%20fired%20at%20his%20family%20of%20workers%20as%20they%20fled%20from%20Lahore.%20Who%20was%20fighting%20whom%20and%20why%3F%20And%20who%20had%20shot%20him%3F%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20or%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20tell.%20We%20only%20gathered%20from%20his%20grunts%20and%20monosyllabic%20answers%20that%20his%20family%20were%20hardcore%20Arya%20Samajis%2C%20and%20they%20would%20take%20revenge%20once%20they%20had%20the%20means.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20a%20tin%20box%20where%20he%20kept%20his%20own%20%E2%80%98revenge%20money%E2%80%99.%20For%20an%20anna%20coin%2C%20he%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20touch%20the%20area%20behind%20his%20ear%20where%20the%20pellet%20was%20still%20lodged.%20He%20hated%20my%20best%20friend%20gentle%20Abdulla%2C%20and%20our%20teacher%20who%20was%20a%20Christian.%20He%20thought%20they%20were%20lesser%20than%20him%20in%20every%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%20and%20a%20year%20later%2C%20my%20father%20was%20transferred%20back%20to%20Nainital.%20But%20much%20before%20I%20learnt%20English%20and%20the%20smart%20catch%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cclash%20of%20civilisations%E2%80%9D%2C%20during%20my%20brief%20sharing%20of%20a%20hard%20school%20bench%20with%20Mohan%20I%20sensed%20that%20even%20when%20everyone%20thought%20the%20war%20was%20over%2C%20lava%20was%20bubbling%20under%20the%20surface%20to%20erupt%20when%20it%20found%20an%20opening.%20Just%20five%20years%20after%20the%20Partition%2C%20the%20refugees%20had%20made%20the%20dreaded%20mosquito-infested%20terai%20area%20bloom%20and%20become%20the%20granary%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20But%20even%20so%2C%20later%20whenever%20unrest%20grew%2C%20one%20heard%20the%20locals%20mutter%20under%20their%20breath%20about%20how%20refugees%20had%20struck%20gold%20but%20retained%20the%20barbarism%20of%20the%20Partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20come%20to%20mind%20watching%20media%20coverage%20of%20POTUS%20embracing%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Israel%2C%20and%20one%20particularly%20obnoxious%20Hindu%20leader%20here%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2023%2F10%2F12%2Fwill-wipe-off-hamas-from-the-face-of-earth-says-hindu-mahasabha-wanting-to-fight-for-israel.html%5C%22%3Eannouncing%20he%20is%20willing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20need%20be%2C%20to%20go%20with%20a%20thousand%20followers%20and%20help%20the%20Israeli%20forces%20take%20revenge%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20quickly%20we%20forget%20the%20lessons%20of%20wars%20past.%20In%20the%20evening%20chat%20shows%20on%20popular%20TV%20channels%2C%20anchors%20and%20their%20screeching%20representatives%20reporting%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20in%20army%20fatigues%20and%20helmets%2C%20behaving%20as%20though%20the%20curtain%20is%20about%20to%20go%20up%20on%20a%20great%20and%20historical%20drama%20in%20which%20they%20are%20actors%20and%20their%20leaders%2C%20though%20far%20away%2C%20are%20decision%20makers.%20The%20mindset%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20had%20perhaps%20been%20glimpsed%20long%20ago%20when%20a%20neighbourhood%20woman%2C%20watching%20Iraq%20being%20hit%20by%20unmanned%20missiles%20on%20her%20TV%20somewhere%20far%2C%20far%20away%20in%20the%20comfort%20of%20her%20home%2C%20had%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9CAh%2C%20what%20a%20beautiful%20war!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Iraq%20and%20its%20terrible%2C%20terrible%20aftermath%2C%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20possible%20(but%20for%20the%20stray%20%3Cem%3Ebhakts%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20see%20modern%20warfare%20as%20a%20brave%20adventure%20whereas%20Krishna%20told%20Arjun%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20win%20you%20shall%20rule%20over%20the%20earth%2C%20if%20you%20die%2C%20you%20shall%20ascend%20to%20heavens.%E2%80%9D%20The%20world%20wars%20have%20already%20killed%20the%20idea%20of%20decisive%20victories%20and%20essential%20nobility%20of%20xenophobic%20patriotism%20fanned%20by%20power%20hungry%20autocrats.%20The%20war%20monuments%20don%E2%80%99t%20commemorate%20victory%20or%20sacrifice%2C%20but%20the%20tragedy%20of%20a%20young%20life%20cut%20short%20at%20its%20prime%20to%20feed%20the%20dreams%20of%20some%20vainglorious%20dreams%20of%20a%20supreme%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20evening%20on%20some%20channel%2C%20how%20silly%20it%20sounded%20to%20hear%20racism%2C%20sexism%20and%20militarism%20all%20in%20one%20quote%20from%20so%20many.%20Whether%20Israeli%20or%20Arab%2C%20the%20young%20soldiers%20I%20saw%20all%20over%20the%20world%20are%20alike.%20They%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20and%20reading%20the%20same%20Hollywood%20westerns%20and%20classics%20about%20war%2C%20drive%20around%20in%20similar%20cars%20or%20dream%20of%20doing%20it%20one%20day%2C%20and%20impress%20beautiful%20maidens%20who%20will%20come%20along%20with%20them%20for%20a%20ride%20and%20a%20drink.%20Despite%20induction%20of%20women%20into%20the%20forces%2C%20one%20can%20fight%20against%20the%20basic%20macho%20culture%20of%20wars%20only%20so%20much.%20Once%20war%20gets%20going%2C%20we%20see%20the%20cave%20man%20come%20out%20and%20then%20its%20all%20hyperventilation%2C%20xenophobic%20and%20religious%20war%20cries%2C%20dragging%20women%20by%20the%20hair%2C%20shooting%20crying%20infants%20and%20curled%20up%20elderly%20too%20weak%20to%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20divides%20the%20world%20in%20Manichean%20dualities%3A%20Black%20or%20White%2C%20Good%20or%20Bad%2C%20Friend%20or%20Foe.%20There%20are%20no%20human%20beings%2C%20only%20shows%2C%20parades%20and%20cries.%20Watching%20the%20gory%20scenes%20from%20a%20bombed%20out%20street%2C%20I%20do%20not%20feel%20it%20is%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20decent%20people%20to%20unite%20that%20the%20perfidious%20coalition%20of%20grey%20haired%20power%20wheeler%20dealers%20say%20it%20is.%20It%20is%20them%2C%20who%20have%20been%20each%20year%20in%20Davos%2C%20Geneva%20and%20New%20York