t%20to%20be%20mostly%20affected%20by%20factors%20such%20as%20industry%2C%20location%2C%20economic%20climate%2C%20connections%20%E2%80%93%20and%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20researchers%20from%20the%20Oxford%20Internet%20Institute%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%2C%20University%20of%20Technology%20Sydney%20(UTS)%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Melbourne%20have%20now%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Bfounder%20personality%20traits%20are%20a%20significant%20feature%20of%20a%20firm's%20ultimate%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20find%20that%20personality%20traits%20don't%20simply%20matter%20for%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20critical%20to%20elevating%20the%20chances%20of%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Paul%20X.%20McCarthy%2C%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20study%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.unsw.edu.au%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-law%2Ffounder-personality-could-predict-start-success-study%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20New%20South%20Wales%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Sydney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20six%20distinct%20personality%20types%20of%20founders%20that%20showed%20an%20increased%20likelihood%20that%20their%20startup%20would%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20types%20were%3A%20fighters%2C%20operators%2C%20accomplishers%2C%20leaders%2C%20experts%2Fengineers%2C%20and%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20personality%20type%20is%20given%20a%20detailed%20breakdown%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20says%20successful%20entrepreneurs%20are%20distinguished%20by%20a%20fondness%20for%20starting%20new%20activities%2C%20novelty%2C%20and%20variety%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20often%20also%20like%20to%20be%20the%20center%20of%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%20these%20core%20personality%20traits%20were%20dramatically%20different%20to%20the%20wider%20population%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20part%20of%20this%20study%2C%20but%20we%20estimate%208%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20worldwide%20may%20have%20personality%20traits%20that%20could%20make%20them%20successful%20founders%2C%26quot%3B%20McCarthy%20said.%20%26quot%3BLikely%2C%20many%20are%20not%20in%20the%20entrepreneurial%20field%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20see%20how%20this%20plays%20out%20in%20many%20notable%20examples%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20adventurousness%20and%20openness%20to%20experience%20of%20Melanie%20Perkins%2C%20the%20assertiveness%20and%20confidence%20of%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%20the%20exuberance%20and%20energy%20of%20Richard%20Branson%2C%20the%20calm%20under%20pressure%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20the%20discipline%20and%20focus%20of%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20and%20the%20trustworthiness%20of%20Larry%20Page%20and%20Sergey%20Brin%20underpin%20their%20company's%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22melanie%20perkins%2C%20Canva%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6533f08bbe9edfa8eda6ccc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22379%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMelanie%20Perkins%20is%20CEO%20of%20Canva.%3Cp%3EHoracio%20Villalobos%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20team%20of%20researchers%20fed%20an%20AI%20algorithm%20with%20the%20language%20and%20activity%20of%2021%2C000%20founder-led%20companies%20gathered%20from%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20analyzing%20their%20characters%20using%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-five-personality-traits-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive-factor%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20personality%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20compared%20these%20profiles%20with%20data%20on%20Crunchbase%20to%20determine%20the%20connection%20between%20personalities%20and%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuccess%20was%20determined%20by%20whether%20a%20company%20had%20been%20acquired%2C%20had%20acquired%20another%20company%2C%20or%20had%20been%20listed%20on%20a%20public%20stock%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20principal%20sources%20of%20data%20used%20in%20the%20study%20%E2%80%94%20Crunchbase%20and%20X%20%E2%80%94%20were%20likely%20to%20contain%20sample%20biases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20model%20also%20confirmed%20that%20a%20diverse%20team%20that%20incorporates%20multiple%20personality%20types%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20increase%20the%20success%20of%20startups.%20In%20particular%2C%20having%20multiple%20founders%20with%20diverse%20personalities%20matters%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreater%20awareness%20of%20this%20novel%20form%20of%20diversity%20may%20help%20create%20more%20resilient%20startups%20capable%20of%20more%20significant%20innovation%20and%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20say%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonality-traits-successful-startup-founders-study-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697968081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6533f05b96f7540cd0627269%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonality-traits-successful-startup-founders-study-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20used%20AI%20to%20determine%20what%20makes%20a%20successful%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20and%20founders'%20personalities%20have%20a%20major%20effect.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonality-traits-successful-startup-founders-study-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hrithik%20wishes%20'Supermom'%20Pinkie%20Roshan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A16979679230