fa8eda2e467%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222834%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWuling%20Hongguang%20Mini%20EVs%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Shanghai%20auto%20expo.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EChina%20has%20led%20the%20world%20in%20production%20and%20sales%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20helped%20by%20government%20subsidies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EChinese%20companies%20focused%20on%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20EV%20batteries%20over%20performance.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20sluggish%20economy%20threatens%20to%20slow%20EV%20sales%20in%20China%2C%20and%20it%20may%20face%20action%20by%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20clear%20winner%20in%20the%20global%20EV%20race%20so%20far%3A%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20second-largest%20economy%20accounted%20for%2064%25%20of%20production%20volume%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2023%2F05%2Felectric-vehicles-ev-sales-growth-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20aided%20by%20government%20subsidies%20and%20tax%20breaks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20producers%20of%20LFP%20(lithium%2C%20iron%2C%20phosphate)%20batteries%20used%20in%20many%20EVs.%20CATL%20is%20China's%20largest%20battery%20manufacturer%20and%20helped%20gain%20the%20top%20spot%20by%20ensuring%20its%20LFP%20batteries%20were%20as%20cheap%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20car%20and%20battery%20makers%20in%20America%20and%20Europe%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bprioritized%20battery%20chemistry%20tied%20to%20performance%2C%20not%20affordability%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20Russo%2C%20Chrysler's%20former%20China%20boss%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F1f95d204-ea6a-4cf3-b66a-952362e8092a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20discovered%20in%20China%20is%20that%20electrification%2C%20and%20the%20democratization%20of%20the%20EV%2C%20prioritizes%20consumer%20affordability.%20By%20making%20it%20cheaper%2C%20China%20wins%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202011%2C%20CATL%20has%20zoomed%20past%20competitors%20from%20South%20Korea%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20Europe%20to%20take%20pole%20position%20with%20its%20batteries%20now%20found%20about%20one%20in%20three%20EVs%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20Ford%20announced%20plans%20to%20use%20CATL%20technology%20in%20a%20new%20%243.5%20billion%20battery%20plant%20in%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPicking%20winners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ariel%20Cohen%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20Eurasia%20Center%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20said%20there's%20been%20considerable%20pushback%20against%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20he%20understood%20%26quot%3Bthe%20national%20security%20imperative%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20uncomfortable%20over%20the%20government%20playing%20favorites%20and%20picking%20winners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20members%20of%20Congress%20are%20concerned%20the%20plant%20could%20leave%20Ford%20reliant%20on%20Chinese%20know-how%20%E2%80%93%20and%20send%20US%20tax%20subsidies%20to%20China.%20Last%20month%20Ford%20paused%20construction%20of%20the%20facility%20amid%20the%20strike%20by%20UAW%20members%2C%20although%20union's%20boss%2C%20Shawn%20Fain%2C%20said%20that%20decision%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bshameful%2C%20barely-veiled%20threat%20by%20Ford%20to%20cut%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Fford-pauses-work-35-billion-battery-plant-michigan-2023-09-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ford%20CEO%20Jim%20Farley%20announcing%20its%20Michigan%20EV%20battery%20plant%20in%20February.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653258bdbe9edfa8eda5a47f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFord%20CEO%20Jim%20Farley%20announcing%20its%20Michigan%20EV%20battery%20plant%20in%20February.%3Cp%3EBill%20Pugliano%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConcern%20about%20using%20Chinese%20battery%20technology%20reflects%20wider%20global%20concern%20about%20China's%20domination%20of%20the%20EV%20battery%20market%2C%20with%20governments%20starting%20to%20block%20Chinese%20investment%20into%20mines%20and%20factories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20the%20Australian%20government%20blocked%20China's%20Yuxiao%20Fund%20from%20increasing%20its%20stake%20in%20rare%20earths%20miner%20Northern%20Minerals%2C%20a%20rare%20earths%20producer%2C%20on%20national%20interest%20grounds%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Faustralia-china-rareearths-idUSKBN2V209R%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustralia%20is%20the%20world's%20biggest%20producer%20of%20lithium%2C%20a%20key%20material%20for%20EV%20batteries%2C%20and%20a%20major%20producer%20of%20other%20rare%20earths.%20Its%20Treasurer%2C%20Jim%20Chalmers%2C%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20Australia%20would%20now%20be%20more%20selective%20about%20who%20could%20invest%20in%20its%20minerals%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20said%20India%20had%20also%20made%20moves%20to%20challenge%20China's%20influence%20and%20that%20he%20expected%20the%20country%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20much%20more%20proactive%20to%20defend%20their%20own%20industry%20and%20other%20players%20against%20Chinese%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20such%20example%20in%20July%2C%20officials%20rejected%20plans%20by%20Chinese%20automaker%20BYD%20for%20a%20%241%20billion%20factory%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223555%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20BYD%20car%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Nanjing%20auto%20show%20in%20China%20this%20month.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65324e7096908fd7cdb36cbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20BYD%20car%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Nanjing%20auto%20show%20in%20China%20this%20month.%3Cp%3ECFOTO%2FFuture%20Publishing%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20%26quot%3Bclear%20advantage%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20field%20also%20reflects%20its%20control%20over%20many%20of%20the%20supply%20chains%20needed%20to%20make%20batteries%2C%20Ilaria%20Mazzocco%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20July%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.morganstanley.com%2Fideas%2Fev-battery-lithium-supply%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bup%20to%2090%25%20of%20the%20EV%20battery%20supply%20chain%20relies%20on%20China%2C%20with%20the%20two%20largest%20Chinese%20battery%20companies%20controlling%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20global%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20bank%20added%20that%20China%20dominated%20%26quot%3Blabor%20and%20manufacturing%20infrastructure%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mining%20of%20critical%20materials%20required%20to%20make%20EVs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20headed%20towards%20a%20world%20where%20governments%20are%20more%20and%20more%20concerned%20about%20globalization-integrated%20supply%20chains%2C%26quot%3B%20Mazzocco%20said%2C%20adding%20this%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20Chinese%20gover