urope%20has%20struggled%20to%20decide%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20imported%20Chinese%20EVs%2C%20but%20Cohen%20said%20it's%20now%20%26quot%3Bshifting%20slowly%20in%20the%20direction%26quot%3B%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20the%20European%20Union%20announced%20an%20investigation%2C%20with%20European%20Commission%20president%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fvon-der-leyen-hits-china-with-electric-vehicle-subsidy-probe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20markets%20are%20now%20flooded%20with%20cheaper%20Chinese%20electric%20cars%26quot%3B%20sold%20at%20artificially%20low%20prices%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20state%20subsidies.%20This%20is%20distorting%20our%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20protests%20in%20Hungary%2C%20where%20CATL%20and%20Mercedes-Benz%20are%20planning%20a%20%247.9%20billion%20battery%20plant%20that%20would%20produce%20enough%20power%20for%20a%20million%20cars%2C%20over%20its%20environmental%20impact%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-01-20%2Fchinese-battery-plant-investment-faces-local-backlash-in-hungary%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20country%20is%20already%20home%20to%20several%20car%20plants%20and%20battery%20factories%20as%20its%20government%20is%20aiming%20to%20make%20Hungary%20a%20big%20EV%20producer.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20also%20thinks%20next%20year's%20US%20presidential%20election%20could%20affect%20Europe's%20stance.%20A%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20could%20accelerate%20any%20EU%20action%20against%20China%20as%20the%20US%20would%20likely%20put%20%26quot%3Bmore%20pressure%20on%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20may%20have%20led%20the%20world%20in%20the%20EV%20race%20%E2%80%93%20but%20those%20days%20could%20well%20be%20numbered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%2