plifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20workers%20monitoring%20the%20area%20when%20it%20detects%20behaviors%20it%20interprets%20as%20suspicious%2C%20which%20multiple%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20told%20Insider%20has%20led%20to%20uncomfortable%20interactions%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmarts-anti-theft-technology-is-effective-but-involves-confronting-customers-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehostile%20confrontations%20with%20customers%20who%20trigger%20the%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20cases%20where%20theft%20is%20suspected%2C%20the%20employees%20told%20Insider%20they%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20accuse%20customers%20of%20stealing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20shoppers%20shared%20experiences%20in%20which%20honest%20mistakes%20or%20technical%20glitches%20resulted%20in%20them%20feeling%20branded%20as%20a%20criminal%2C%20whether%20by%20store%20workers%2C%20local%20law%20enforcement%2C%20or%20even%20the%20technology%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20continuously%20working%20on%20our%20security%20processes%2C%20and%20we%20encourage%20customers%20with%20concerns%20to%20let%20us%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Walmart%20spokesperson%20Joe%20Pennington%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOur%20associates%20are%20trained%20to%20handle%20these%20situations%20professionally%20and%20respectfully%2C%20ensuring%20our%20customers%20have%20the%20best%20shopping%20experience%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20Baker%20was%20pregnant%20and%20hurriedly%20shopping%20with%20her%204-year-old%20in%20tow%20when%20her%20kiosk%20kept%20intermittently%20freezing%20up%20over%20a%20missed%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20retail%20worker%20herself%2C%20she%20tried%20slowing%20down%20the%20pace%20to%20see%20if%20that%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20a%20manager%2C%20she%20eventually%20discovered%20the%20system%20was%20noticing%20her%20wallet%2C%20which%20was%20tucked%20in%20her%20armpit%2C%20and%20flagging%20it%20as%20unscanned%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20doesn't%20even%20sell%20the%20same%20wallet%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShopper%20Daniel%20Jones%20told%20Insider%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bappalled%26quot%3B%20when%20his%20kiosk%20lit%20up%20and%20began%20playing%20security%20video%20footage%20of%20an%20alleged%20missed%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20did%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20being%20accused%20of%20a%20crime%2C%20I%20felt%20confused%20and%20upset%20because%20I%20was%20in%20my%20work%20uniform%20and%20other%20people%20may%20see%20the%20video%20playback%20and%20think%20that%20I'm%20stealing%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaiting%20for%20an%20employee%20to%20come%20over%2C%20question%20him%2C%20and%20reactivate%20his%20system%20made%20Jones%20feel%20like%20he%20was%20being%20%26quot%3Bpunished%26quot%3B%20for%20using%20the%20available%20hand%20scanner%20to%20ring%20up%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Bisbee's%20missed-scan%20alert%20was%20also%20related%20to%20his%20use%20of%20the%20handheld%20scanner.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20episode%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20Jones%20said%20he%20has%20seen%20two%20other%20shoppers%20apparently%20caught%20off-guard%20and%20become%20defensive%20over%20the%20missed-scan%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20make%20the%20honest%20shopper%20feel%20unwelcome%2C%20and%20feel%20like%20they%20are%20being%20treated%20like%20thieves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20Walmart%20worker%20or%20shopper%20who%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20perspective%2C%20please%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adreuter%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EDominick%20via%20email.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20Insider%20strongly%20recommends%20using%20a%20personal%20email%20an