s)%20and%20Mr%20Yadav%20has%20been%20asserting%20that%20PDA%20will%20defeat%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20message%20with%20the%20post%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%202024%20elections%20will%20be%20PDA's%20revolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcrimony%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Congress%20announced%20a%20list%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20%26quot%3Bfooling%26quot%3B%20other%20parties%20and%20even%20hinted%20that%20had%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20known%20the%20alliance%20doesn't%20work%20on%20state%20level%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20so%20open%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20assured%20us%20that%20they%20will%20think%20about%20us%20for%20six%20seats.%20When%20they%20announced%20candidates%20there%20was%20nothing%20for%20SP.%20If%20I%20knew%20there%20was%20no%20alliance%20on%20state%2C%20then%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20met.%20We%20wouldn't%20have%20spoken%20to%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20these%20comments%2C%20Congress%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20President%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20said%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EArre%20bhai%20chhodo%3C%2Fem%3E%20Akhilesh%20Vakhilesh...%20(leave%20this%20Akhilesh%20Vakhilesh).%20The%20Congress%20state%20unit%20had%20asserted%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20at%20the%20central%20level%20and%20its%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20clearly%20miffed%20SP%20chief%20continued%20to%20attack%20the%20Congress%20on%20Friday%2C%20asking%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20behaves%20like%20this%2C%20who%20will%20stand%20with%20them%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20%26quot%3Bbetray%26quot%3B%20the%20Samajwadi%20party%20and%20asked%20it%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20whether%20it%20wanted%20an%20alliance%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20received%20a%20message%20from%20someone%20through%20the%20senior-most%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20If%20he%20is%20saying%20something%2C%20I%20will%20have%20to%20follow.%20He%20gave%20some%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%2C%20without%20revealing%20any%20name%20or%20explaining%20further.%20%26quot%3BBut%20one%20thing%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%3A%20why%20did%20they%20call%20us%20if%20they%20did%20not%20want%20an%20alliance%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20conspire%20against%20us%2C%20don't%20betray%20us.%20They%20should%20tell%20us%20straight%20that%20they%20don't%20need%20Samajwadis.%20I%20promise%20you%20that%20we%20will%20not%20talk%20about%20alliance%20even%20once%20and%20will%20begin%20preparation%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20on%20our%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20support%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20miracle%20that%20the%20party%20wanted%20it%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20same%20Congress%20party%20that%20did%20not%20give%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20caste%20census%20earlier.%20Now%20everyone%20knows%20that%20until%20and%20unless%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20support%20of%20the%20backward%20castes%20and%20tribes%2C%20you%20won't%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20miracle%20that%20now%20the%20Congress%20party%20wants%20a%20caste%20census.%20Congress%20party%20is%20now%20aware%20that%20the%20vote%20they%20were%20searching%20for%20is%20not%20with%20them%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697961540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F0ooe06v_akhilesh-yadav-650-_625x300_21_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-days-of-digs-ak