20US%20District%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleging%20violations%20of%20human%20trafficking%20and%20wage%20law%20against%20BAPS.%20The%20workers%20said%20that%20they%20were%20confined%20and%20forced%20to%20work%20for%20about%20%241%20per%20hour%20on%20constructing%20the%20massive%20Swaminarayan%20temple.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20organisation%20made%20them%20work%20for%20as%20much%20as%2087%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20when%20New%20Jersey%E2%80%99s%20minimum%20wage%20is%20%2412%20an%20hour%20and%20US%20law%20requires%20the%20pay%20rate%20for%20most%20hourly%20workers%20to%20rise%20to%20time-and-a-half%20when%20they%20work%20more%20than%2040%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20on%20their%20construction%20jobs%2C%20the%20complaint%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20were%20forced%20to%20live%20and%20work%20in%20a%20fenced%2C%20guarded%20compound%20which%20they%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20unaccompanied%20by%20overseers%20affiliated%20with%20(BAPS).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20workers%20belong%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20US%20as%20%E2%80%98religious%20workers%20and%20volunteers%E2%80%99.%20Following%20the%20allegations%2C%20US%20federal%20authorities%20had%20raided%20the%20construction%20site%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fdalit-workers-allege-shocking-violations-in-building-hindu-temple-in-new-jersey%5C%22%3EDalit%20Workers%20Allege%20%E2%80%98Shocking%20Violations%E2%80%99%20in%20Building%20Temple%20in%20New%20Jersey%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20lawsuit%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fupdated-lawsuit-against-baps-alleges-use-of-forced-labour-at-more-temple-sites-across-us%5C%22%3Eupdated%20to%20add%20that%20BAPS%20had%20flouted%20labour%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20just%20at%20the%20temple%20in%20New%20Jersey%20but%20at%20other%20temple%