20was%20known%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20and%20military%20officials%20soon%20after%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20began%20in%20February%202022%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Moscow%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20realistically%20sustain%20India%E2%80%99s%20sizeable%20defence%20equipment%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20defence%20industry%20official.%20It%E2%80%99s%20now%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20he%20declared%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccrunch%20time%E2%80%9D%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20atamnirbhar%20initiative%20to%20indigenise%20its%20weaponry%20requirements%20and%20rapidly%20reduce%20dependency%20on%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20remains%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20military%20hardware%20supplier%2C%20with%20over%2065%25%20of%20its%20current%20assets%20like%20fighters%2C%20helicopters%2C%20submarines%2C%20tanks%20and%20infantry%20combat%20vehicles%2C%20varied%20missiles%2C%20ammunition%20and%20ordnance%20sourced%20from%20Moscow.%20According%20to%20the%20Stockholm%20International%20Peace%20Research%20Institute%20(SIPRI)%2C%20India%20had%20acquired%20%2439%20billion%20worth%20of%20materiel%20from%20Russia%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20either%20imported%20directly%20or%20licence-built%20domestically%20through%20a%20transfer%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20recent%20months%20India%E2%80%99s%20military%2C%20despite%20a%20sanguine%20fa%C3%A7ade%2C%20has%20been%20confronted%20with%20grave%20uncertainty%20and%20delays%20over%20deliveries%20of%20Russian%20materiel%20and%20spares%2C%20as%20both%20sides%20had%20struggled%20to%20evolve%20a%20dependable%20payment%C2%A0structure%20that%20was%20not%20violative%20of%20US-led%20sanctions%20on%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F22184843%2FSukhoi_Su-30MKI_India_-_Air_Force_AN1234411.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F22184843%2FSukhoi_Su-30MKI_India_-_Air_Force_AN1234411.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F22184843%2FSukhoi_Su-30MKI_India_-_Air_Force_AN1234411-300x157.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-609482%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22535%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20Sukhoi%20Su-30MKI%20aircraft.%20Photo%3A%20Mike%20Freer%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20GFDL%201.2%20or%20GFDL%201.2%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20claimed%20that%20over%20%243%20billion%20owed%20to%20Russia%20by%20India%20for%20an%20assortment%20of%20platforms%2C%20spares%20and%20related%20apparatus%20for%20in-service%20equipment%20had%20accumulated%20over%2012-14%20months%20leading%20to%20Moscow%20%E2%80%98pausing%E2%80%99%20all%20further%20credit%20to%20Delhi%20for%20its%20defence%20buys.%20The%20rupees%20that%20had%20piled%20up%20under%20the%20mutually%20agreed%20rupee-rouble%20payment%20protocol%20had%20been%20routed%20via%20%E2%80%98vostro%E2%80%99%20accounts%20through%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Sherbank%20and%20VTB%20Bank%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20late%202022%20this%20state%20of%20affairs%20has%20been%20roiled%20further%20by%20massive%20payments%2C%20also%20in%20rupees%2C%20for%20Russian%20oil%20imports%20which%20had%20increased%2050-fold%20after%20the%20Ukraine%20invasion.%20Last%20month%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20reiterated%20that%20Moscow%20faced%20the%20problem%20of%20a%20rupee%20surfeit%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wionews.com%2Fbusiness-economy%2Findia-to-offer-russia-to-invest-trapped-rupees-serei-lavrov-634749%3Futm_source%3Dground.news%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cnot%20currently%20usable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%20that%20these%20rupees%20needed%20%E2%80%9Ctransferring%E2%80%9D%20to%20another%20currency%2C%20and%20that%20an%20alternate%20arrangement%20was%20under%20discussion%20with%20his%20counterpart%20S.%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20also%20conceded%20that%20there%20was%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F36496%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cunderstandable%20concern%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20trade%20imbalance%20between%20Russia%20and%20India%20for%20defence%20equipment%20and%20told%20the%20India-Russia%20Business%20Dialogue%20in%20Delhi%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20needed%20to%20cooperate%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20urgent%20basis%E2%80%9D%20to%20address%20this%20predicament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20India%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findia-uncomfortable-with-russias-demand-that-it-pays-for-oil-bills-in-chinese-yuan-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20down%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20proposal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20settle%20its%20oil%20bills%20%E2%80%93%20and%20possibly%2C%20even%20its%20military%20equipment%20outstandings%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Chinese%20yuan.%20But%20alongside%2C%20it%20had%20seemingly%20also%20not%20finalised%20a%20workable%20solution%20to%20this%20predicament%2C%20as%20Indian%20banks%20continued%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98wary%E2%80%99%20of%20exploring%20other%20forms%20of%20payments%20to%20Russia%2C%20via%20other%20currencies%2C%20for%20fear%20of%20inviting%20secondary%20sanctions%20from%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffear-of-us-sanctions-payment-method-issues-stall-russias-military-supply-to-india-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20had%20even%20proposed%20that%20Russia%20utilise%20the%20rupees%20from%20its%20weapon%20sales%20to%20invest%20in%20Indian%20debt%20and%20capital%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Moscow%20rejected%20the%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Frussian-exporters-vostro-facility-rupees-indian-markets%5C%22%3EWhy%20Russian%20Exporters%20Are%20Reluctant%20to%20Use%20Vostro%20Facility%20to%20Invest%20Rupees%20in%20Indian%20Markets%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20enduring%20payment%20crunch%2C%20according%20to%20senior%20Indian%20defence%20officials%2C%20had%20adversely%20impacted%20the%20already%20deferred%20delivery%20of%20two%20of%20five%20Almaz-Antey%20S-400%20Triumf%20self-propelled%20surface-to-air%20missile%20systems%20and%20four%20Admiral%20Grigorovich%20Project%201135.6M%20frigates%20%E2%80%93%20two%20of%20which%20were%20to%20be%20constructed%20indigenously%2C%20under%20a%20transfer%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%243%20billion%20leasing%20of%20another%20Project%20971%20%E2%80%98Akula%E2%80%99%20(Schuka-B)-class%20nuclear-powered%20submarine%20and%20providing%20some%2070%2C000%20Kalashnikov%20AK-203%207.62x39mm%20assault%20rifles%2C%20ahead%20of%20local%20licence%20building%20601%2C427%20of%20them%2C%20too%20were%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%2C%20however%2C%20have%20had%20some%20past%20commercial%20experience%20in%20bypassing%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202019%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20VTB%20Bank%20reportedly%20signed%20currency%20deals%20with%20counterparts%20in%20India%20and%20China%20in%20a%20deft%20manoeuvre%20to%20dodge%20the%20Washington-imposed%20Countering%20America%E2%80%99s%20Adversaries%20Through%20Sanctions%20Act%20or%20CAATSA%20in%202017%20that%20embargoed%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20defence%20industry%20following%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20take-over%20of%20Crimea%20and%20its%20alleged%20interference%20in%20the%202016%20US%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EIzvestia%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20payment%20method%20included%20the%20application%20of%20%E2%80%98gateways%E2%80%99%20to%20circumvent%20the%20international%20Society%20for%20Worldwide%20Interbank%20Financial%20Telecommunication%20or%20SWIFT%20banking%20system%20which%20now%20stands%20sanctioned%20for%20Russia.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20India%E2%80%99s%20arrangement%20with%20VTB%20still%20persisted%20and%20if%20so%2C%20whether%20it%20could%20be%20exploited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20year%20earlier%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fspecial-report%2Fstory%2F20181001-ballet-with-the-bear-1344295-2018-09-22%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20August%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20and%20Rosonboronexport%20had%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20by%20which%20the%20public%20sector%20Syndicate%20Bank%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20unexposed%20to%20US%20banking%20or%20financial%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20agreed%20to%20directly%20transfer%20rupees%2Froubles%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Sberbank%2C%20doing%20away%20with%20normally%20routine%20letters%20of%20credit%20or%20LCs.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20the%20equivalent%20of%20%2440%20million%20was%20transferred%20in%20rupees%2Froubles%20in%20September%202019%20as%20payment%20for%20the%20retrofit%20of%20one%20Indian%20Navy%20%E2%80%98Kilo%E2%80%99-class%20boat.%20Sberbank%20has%20since%20been%20sanctioned%2C%20foreclosing%20it%20thereby%20as%20an%20alternative%20payment%20route%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20mid-1960s%20India%20acquired%20over%20%2470%20billion%20worth%20of%20weaponry%20and%20related%20defence%20gear%20from%20Moscow.%20Till%20around%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20this%20military%20commerce%20was%20conducted%20via%20the%20rupee-rouble%20route%20and%20through%20barter%3B%20India%20supplied%20Moscow%20tea%2C%20sugar%2C%20toothpaste%2C%20footwear%2C%20socks%20and%20other%20similar%20food%20and%20everyday%20items%20that%20were%20then%20in%20short%20supply%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%20In%20exchange%2C%20India%20received%20combat%20platforms%20like%20fighters%2C%20helicopters%2C%20transport%20aircraft%2C%20tanks%2C%20submarines%20and%20warships.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Soviet%20Union%E2%80%99s%20break-up%20in%201991%2C%20Russia%20and%20India%20switched%20over%20to%20trading%20in%20US%20dollars.%20After%20protracted%20negotiations%20lasting%20several%20years%20the%20two%20%E2%80%98rationalised%E2%80%99%20India%E2%80%99s%20rupee-rouble%20debt%20and%20other%20past%20financial%20discrepancies%20in%20an%20eventual%20settlement%20around%201996%2C%20determining%20that%20India%20owed%20Russia%20around%20%2450%20million.%20The%20deadline%20for%20reimbursing%20this%20hoary%20liability%20was%20fixed%20at%202037%20but%20remains%20bedevilled%20by%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20with%20Rosonboronexport%20now%20expressing%20its%20inability%2C%20albeit%20subtly%2C%20to%20provide%20defence%20equipment%20to%20its%20overseas%20clients%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20India%20remains%20by%20far%20the%20biggest%E2%80%93%20knotty%20issues%20of%20payments%20could%2C%20in%20time%2C%20be%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%3B%20though%20this%20process%20will%20likely%20take%20more%20than%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697960227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F06124540%2FIAF_LCH-Image2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftop-arms-vendor-admits-russian-defence-industry-facing-pressing-challenges-seeks-new-export-format%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20press%20statement%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20joint%20stock%20arms%20export%20company%20Rosonboronexport%20has%20admitted%20it%20needs%20to%20prioritise%20%26quot%3Bmanufacturing%20and%20supplying%20products%20to%20the%20Russian%20Army%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftop-arms-vendor-admits-russian-defence-industry-facing-pressing-challenges-seeks-new-export-format%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20First%20Sights%20and%20Sounds%20of%20War%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22123058%2Fjerusalem.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20morning%20of%20October%207%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20I%20wake%20up%20to%20a%20loud%20siren.%20Despite%20never%20having%20heard%20it%20before%2C%20I%20know%20what%20it%20means.%20My%20roommates%20and%20I%20rush%20out%20of%20the%20house%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bomb%20shelter.%20I%20had%20seen%20signs%20with%20arrows%20that%20say%20%E2%80%9CSHELTER%E2%80%9D%20around%20my%20house%2C%20but%20I%20never%20tried%20to%20check%20where%20the%20shelter%20is%20exactly%20or%20what%20it%20looks%20like.%20These%20signs%20are%20everywhere%20in%20Israel%3B%20when%20I%20first%20saw%20them%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20what%20they%20implied%3A%20infrastructure%20of%20war%20is%20mundane%20here.%20Just%20like%20there%20are%E2%80%9CExit%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CBathroom%E2%80%9D%20signs%2C%20there%20are%20bomb%20shelter%20signs.%20Is%20anyone%20talking%20about%20what%20it%20would%20take%20to%20not%20need%20bomb%20shelters%20everywhere%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20stopped%20noticing%20the%20bomb%20shelters%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20just%20like%20many%20other%20things%20which%20became%20normalised.%20Israelis%20with%20big%20guns%20strolling%20with%20their%20families%20at%20the%20mall.%20Young%20people%20in%20military%20uniform%20and%20giant%20backpacks%20sitting%20on%20the%20bus%2C%20going%20for%20military%20service.%20Militarised%20police%20vehicles%20on%20the%20roads%20with%20their%20sirens%20and%20emergency%20lights%20on%20perpetually.%20Surveillance%20cameras%20in%20all%20public%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shelter%20is%20locked%2C%20and%20no%20neighbours%20bothered%20coming%20outside%20their%20houses%20on%20hearing%20the%20siren.%20The%20siren%20had%20stopped%20by%20now%2C%20and%20the%20sky%20looked%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20no%20traces%20of%20a%20rocket%20trail.%20Why%20would%20someone%20lock%20the%20shelter%2C%20though%3F%20A%20neighbour%20explains%20that%20the%20shelter%20has%20been%20used%20as%20an%20art%20workshop%20or%20something%2C%20and%20the%20person%20running%20it%20had%20been%20keeping%20it%20locked.%20We%20%E2%80%93%20three%20internationals%20%E2%80%93%20talk%20to%20a%20few%20neighbours%20to%20find%20the%20key.%20Nobody%20seems%20alarmed.%20Many%20people%20here%20are%20used%20to%20the%20siren%20warnings%20of%20rockets%20from%20Gaza.%20An%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20these%20rockets%20are%20intercepted%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20and%20never%20land%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20neighbours%20had%20clearly%20not%20checked%20social%20media.%20There%20were%20unbelievable%20videos%20showing%20that%20somehow%20militants%20from%20Gaza%20had%20entered%20Israel.%20How%20could%20that%20be%3F%20Gaza%20is%20surrounded%20by%20walls%20and%20a%20highly%20sophisticated%20system%20of%20cameras%2C%20sensors%20and%20Israeli%20military%20personnel%20on%20guard.%20I%20thought%20that%20breaking%20through%20the%20walls%20or%20the%20checkpoint%20crossing%20was%20an%20impossibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bomb%20shelter%20door%20was%20opened%20later%20that%20day.%20It%20is%20huge%3B%20it%20has%20an%20air%20conditioner%2C%20and%20even%20toilets.%20This%20is%20a%20fancy%20neighbourhood%2C%20so%20of%20course%20human%20lives%20here%20are%20treated%20as%20if%20they%20deserve%20more.%20In%20southern%20Israel%2C%20in%20the%20villages%20in%20the%20desert%20and%20in%20poor%20neighbourhoods%2C%20there%20are%20not%20enough%20shelters.%20What%20about%20shelters%20in%20Gaza%3F%20There%20is%20certainly%20no%20Iron%20Dome%20to%20intercept%20Israeli%20missiles%20falling%20on%20Gazans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20forwards%20a%20text%20message.%20It%20is%20from%20Khalil%20from%20Gaza%2C%20who%20teaches%20English%2C%20and%20is%20very%20passionate%20about%20literature%20and%20poetry.%20He%20dreams%20of%20travelling%20outside%20Gaza%20and%20doing%20a%20PhD.%20His%20thoughts%20on%20justice%2C%20peace%20and%20occupation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20descriptions%20of%20his%20life%20within%20the%20walls%20of%20Gaza%2C%20have%20touched%20so%20many%20people%20outside%20those%20walls.%20He%20is%20deeply%20loved%20by%20so%20many.%20The%20text%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CGreat%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20I%20evacuated%20my%20house%20and%20Israel%20has%20already%20started%20to%20attack%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20is%20in%20tears.%20The%20scale%20of%20the%20attack%20orchestrated%20by%20Hamas%20is%20becoming%20clearer%20with%20every%20passing%20moment%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20already%3A%20Gaza%20will%20be%20bombed%20much%20more%20severely%20than%20it%20has%20been%20in%20recent%20years.%20Khalil%20will%20have%20to%20find%20safe%20places%20within%20Gaza.%20He%20sends%20another%20text%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20heart%20and%20the%20warmth%20of%20the%20love%20of%20my%20friends%20is%20the%20real%20shelter%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20are%20checking%20on%20him%20periodically%20and%20sharing%20updates%20on%20a%20group%20chat.%20Every%20update%20about%20him%2C%20or%20lack%20thereof%2C%20is%20making%20me%20anxious.%20Another%20friend%20on%20this%20group%20writes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20people%20help%20me%20think%20of%20more%20poems%20about%20steadfastness%2C%20love%20and%20resilience%20in%20struggle%2C%20love%20and%20solidarity%2C%20or%20anything%20that%20feels%20right%3F%20If%20you%20send%20them%20here%20I%E2%80%99ll%20pass%20them%20on%20from%20us%20and%20tell%20Khalil%20we%E2%80%99re%20thinking%20of%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Denial%2C%20Deception%20and%20Distortion%3A%20The%20'Atrocity%20Propaganda'%20War%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20Conflict%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdenial-deception-and-distortion-the-atrocity-propaganda-war-in-israel-and-palestine%5C%22%3EDenial%2C%20Deception%20and%20Distortion%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Atrocity%20Propaganda%E2%80%99%20War%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20Conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20major%20escalation%20between%20Israel%20and%20Gaza%20was%20in%202021.%20Aside%20from%20rockets%20and%20airstrikes%20there%20were%20massive%20riots%20and%20police%20violence.%20Settlers%20and%20the%20Israeli%20law%20enforcement%20went%20on%20a%20rampage%20in%20East%20Jerusalem%2C%20which%20is%20predominantly%20Palestinian%20and%20under%20the%20Israeli%20occupation.%20A%20Palestinian-Jewish%20couple%2C%20who%20are%20friends%20of%20mine%2C%20lived%20through%20this%20horror%20and%20witnessed%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20Palestinians%20were%20targeted%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20Sheikh%20Jarrah.%20Sometimes%20when%20I%20talk%20to%20them%20about%20the%20political%20situation%20here%20I%20feel%20like%20they%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20humanity%2C%20and%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20events%20in%202021.%20I%20hope%20this%20changes%20or%20that%20I%20am%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWould%20Jerusalem%20be%20up%20in%20flames%20again%20because%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20this%20morning%3F%20Sirens%20warn%20of%20incoming%20rockets%20from%20Gaza%2C%20but%20not%20of%20a%20mob%20of%20settlers%20seeking%20revenge%20from%20Palestinians.%20Should%20I%20go%20stay%20with%20my%20friends%20in%20the%20Tel%20Aviv%20area%2C%20where%20there%20are%20more%20rockets%20but%20lesser%20chances%20of%20civilian%20violence%3F%20Dealing%20with%20sirens%20and%20rockets%20seems%20easier%20than%20worrying%20that%20strangers%20on%20the%20streets%20can%20suddenly%20turn%20violent%20towards%20me%20because%20of%20how%20they%20construe%20my%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22123219%2FWestern-Wall-and-Al-Aqsa-in-the-Old-City.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22123219%2FWestern-Wall-and-Al-Aqsa-in-the-Old-City.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22123219%2FWestern-Wall-and-Al-Aqsa-in-the-Old-City-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22123219%2FWestern-Wall-and-Al-Aqsa-in-the-Old-City-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWestern%20Wall%20and%20Al%20Aqsa%20in%20Jerusalem%E2%80%99s%20Old%20City.%20Photo%3A%20Aman%20Abhishek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20dark%2C%20the%20streets%20of%20Jerusalem%20are%20unusually%20empty%2C%20shops%20are%20closed%2C%20and%20there%20is%20police%20everywhere.%20I%20am%20close%20to%20the%20bus%20station%20and%20a%20small%20crowd%20has%20gathered%20for%20some%20reason.%20I%20see%20two%20Palestinian%20men%20surrounded%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20police.%20The%20first%20is%20showing%20the%20contents%20of%20his%20bag%20as%20the%20police%20are%20checking%20his%20ID.%20The%20other%20man%20has%