%2F21211940%2FScreenshot-2023-10-21-at-9.16.51.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Speaking%20at%20a%20FICCI%20event%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20said%20that%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20India%20stood%20at%20111th%20out%20of%20125%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1715021411683598388%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewas%20compiled%20by%20calling%203%2C000%20people%20in%20India%20and%20asking%20if%20they%20were%20hungry.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-ranks-111th-among-125-countries-in-global-hunger-index-report%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20report%20makers%E2%80%99%20summary%20rejection%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20assertions.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20what%20also%20garnered%20outrage%20was%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20she%20had%20had%20a%20trying%20day%20and%20that%20she%20would%20have%20also%20said%20she%20was%20hungry%20had%20she%20been%20called%20on%20the%20phone%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20has%20called%20Irani%20out%20for%20her%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitivity%E2%80%9D%20and%20for%20making%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%20of%20hunger%2C%E2%80%9D%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20Index%20functions%20this%20way%20is%20not%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20what%20Irani%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20that%20makes%20headlines%20now%2C%20many%20a%20people%20have%20said%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20hogwash.%20How%20do%20they%20build%20that%20indice%3F%203%2C000%20people%20in%20a%20country%20of%20a%20140%20crore%20get%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20Gallup%20and%20they%20are%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%98Are%20you%20hungry%3F%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWriting%20for%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Banjot%20Kaur%20had%20noted%20in%20her%20report%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20rejected%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20October%2012%20statement%2C%20the%20government%20had%20questioned%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalhungerindex.org%2Fmethodology.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20selection%20of%20the%20four%20parameters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20which%20is%20the%20opinion%20poll%20Irani%20referred%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaur%20quoted%20the%20government%20as%20having%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CThree%20out%20of%20the%20four%20indicators%20used%20for%20calculation%20of%20the%20index%20are%20related%20to%20the%20health%20of%20children%20and%20cannot%20be%20representative%20of%20the%20entire%20population.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20assertion%20makes%20one%20aspect%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20which%20contradicts%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20%E2%80%9Chow%20they%20build%20that%E2%80%9D%20index%3A%20it%20depends%20on%20four%20parameters%2C%20not%20the%20single%20one%20on%20the%20opinion%20poll%2C%20as%20she%20indicated%20in%20the%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERight%20afterwards%2C%20Irani%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20trust%20me%2C%20I%20have%20left%20my%20house%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20morning%20at%204%20today.%20I%20got%20a%20flight%20at%205%20to%20go%20to%20Kochi.%20I%20did%20a%20conclave%20there.%20Got%20a%20flight%20at%205%20o%E2%80%99clock%20to%20come%20to%20this%20programme.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20get%20to%20anything%20called%20food%2C%20it%20will%20be%2010%20o%E2%80%99clock.%20If%20you%20would%20have%20called%20me%20anytime%20during%20the%20day%20today%20and%20asked%20from%20Gallup%2C%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20hungry%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%E2%80%99ll%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9COh%20yes%2C%20I%20am.%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20call%20that%20Irani%20claims%20she%20would%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20attend%20while%20hungry%20aims%20to%20fix%20the%20%E2%80%98Proportion%20of%20Undernourished%E2%80%99%20or%20PoU%20population.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20based%20on%20an%20opinion%20poll%20conducted%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20small%20sample%20size%20of%203000.%E2%80%9D%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20reservations%20are%20in%20line%20with%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Kaur%20writes%20in%20her%20report%2C%20the%20GHI%20report%20makers%2C%20in%20an%20emailed%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20October%2013%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20PoU%20rate%20is%20just%20one-third%20of%20the%20total%20GHI%20score.%20More%20importantly%20for%20the%20scope%20of%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20assertions%2C%20the%20PoU%20is%20arrived%20from%20the%20study%20of%20several%20underlying%20parameters%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eand%20not%20just%20from%20the%20opinion%20poll.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Index%20considered%20food%20balance%20reports%20that%2C%20Kaur%20reports%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20emailed%20responses%2C%C2%A0was%20partly%20arrived%20at%20%3Cem%3Eusing%20data%20sources%20officially%20given%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20itself.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIrani%20is%20thus%20publicly%20commenting%20against%20her%20own%20government%E2%80%99s%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20India%E2%80%99s%20latest%20relevant%20data%20was%20collected%20in%202011%2C%20the%20distribution%20of%20calorie%20intake%20in%20the%20population%20was%20estimated%20using%20the%20Food%20Insecurity%20Experience%20Scale%20(FIES)%20survey%20data%2C%20for%20which%20the%20Gallup%20World%20Poll%20was%20used%2C%20the%20report%20makers%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20this%20poll%20was%20part%20of%20an%20indicator%20which%20was%20a%20part%20of%20four%20indicators%20which%20ultimately%20contributed%20to%20the%20Index%20score.%20And%20not%20the%20sole%20indicator%2C%20as%20Irani%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20claim%20is%20also%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20rendered%20false%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20objections%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eother%3C%2Fem%3E%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20indicating%20at%20least%20that%20there%20are%20other%20indicators.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20other%20government%20has%20disputed%20the%20GHI%E2%80%99s%20methodology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIrani%20also%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20that%20indice%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E)%20says%20Pakistan%20is%20better%20than%20India.%20Can%20you%20imagine%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Index%2C%20Pakistan%20does%20rank%20above%20India.%20At%20102%2C%20it%20is%20nine%20spots%20above%20India.%20But%20in%20many%20categories%2C%20its%20performance%20is%20comparable%20to%20India%E2%80%99s.%20Its%20percentage%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20child%20stunting%20(37.6%25)%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20similar%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20(35.5%25).%20The%20Index%20reports%20notes%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20floods%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20crops%2C%20which%20directly%20affect%20food%20consumption.%20It%20also%20pays%20attention%20to%20Indian%20farmers%E2%80%99%20particular%20struggles%2C%20without%20attempting%20to%20compare%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20video%20offers%20a%20deeper%20dive%20into%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fqvh82sP4FhM%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20India%20Ranks%20111%20Out%20of%20125%20Countries%20in%20Hunger%3F%20%7C%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20Report%20%7C%20Indian%20Government%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697903474000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21211940%2FScreenshot-2023-10-21-at-9.16.51.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%