20near%20our%20village%20where%20we%20host%20several%20drives%20to%20sensitise%20the%20children%20about%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20wildlife%2C%20and%20nature%20conservation.%20They%20are%20the%20future%20of%20the%20society%3B%20reaching%20out%20to%20them%20is%20my%20way%20of%20making%20their%20future%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunando%20has%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20make%20the%20place%20a%20sustainable%20one%20not%20just%20for%20humans%20but%20for%20animals%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20cameras%20set%20up%20all%20around%20the%20place%2C%20and%20I%20observe%20the%20videos%20to%20locate%20any%20sightings.%20If%20there%20are%20sightings%20too%20close%20to%20civilisation%2C%20we%20alert%20the%20authorities%20so%20the%20animals%20can%20be%20safely%20relocated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunando%20informs%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20sees%20the%20place%20as%20a%20home%20not%20just%20for%20himself%20but%20for%20the%20animals%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Opening%20our%20home%20to%20wildlife%20lovers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunando%20shares%20that%20initially%2C%20he%20had%20no%20plans%20of%20converting%20his%20home%20into%20a%20homestay.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20moved%20into%20the%20place%20in%202011%20and%20have%20lived%20here%20ever%20since.%20Whenever%20we%20would%20host%20our%20friends%2C%20they%20would%20insist%20we%20share%20it%20with%20others%20too.%20There%20was%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20land%20on%20our%20property%20too%2C%20so%20we%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuTHMcIvX44%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuTHMcIvX44%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_