ndia.com%2F153182%2Findian-food-unique-fermented-dishes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20delicacies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Raj%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20opened%2C%20our%20guests%20loved%20learning%20about%20India.%20They%20would%20enjoy%20listening%20to%20Indian%20music%2C%20its%20artwork%2C%20and%20cuisines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBombay-Mahal-3-1697638027.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Once%20scared%20to%20try%20Indian%20food%2C%20today%20hundreds%20of%20local%20customers%20from%20Maine%20relish%20food%20at%20Bombay%20Mahal.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBombay-Mahal-3-1697638027.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBombay-Mahal-3-1697638027-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBombay-Mahal-3-1697638027-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBombay-Mahal-3-1697638027-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBombay-Mahal-3-1697638027-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332541%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOnce%20scared%20to%20try%20Indian%20food%2C%20today%20hundreds%20of%20local%20customers%20from%20Maine%20relish%20food%20at%20Bombay%20Mahal.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20here%20embraced%20our%20food%20right%20from%20the%20start%20and%20were%20very%20keen%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20India%20and%20our%20culture.%20They%20also%20asked%20how%20they%20could%20make%20some%20of%20these%20foods%20at%20home